{"tid":1360091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱烈歡迎老解蒞臨香港","createTime":"2019-07-24T09:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T09:41:37.000Z","uid":127202,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e31bee087fad676d36ec94c9f33bac5b8da9d5b","tid":1360091,"uid":127202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:28:43.000Z","msg":"日日OT到凌晨  生活係乜朋友係乜  更莫講話女朋友<br />\n人工又唔加   到真係有得加又得雞碎咁多  物價又高  儲極唔夠買樓<br />\n富人愈富 貧者愈貧 有希望嘅人生僅限於有父幹有家底嘅人<br />\n對住藍絲老豆老母又好似困獸鬥咁 租金高企走唔到出去自住<br />\n喺屋企抖啖氣喊下嘅空間都無   要話落街買啲野先去後樓梯到喊<br />\n星期六日想話出去行下街咩  想練障礙賽咪去囉<br />\n香港特色愈黎愈唔鮮明 十八區商場幾乎一式一樣  行黎行去咪又係咁<br />\n好啦咁想去郊區呼吸下新鮮空氣發覺原來行山都要排隊<br />\n離島區早已淪為蝗嘅免費酒店    開曬帳篷嘈淵巴閉<br />\n喺香港係生存唔係生活   係一啖氣都唔容許俾你輕鬆抖<br />\n<br />\n老共以為我地恃住自己身嬌肉貴咩  都有嘅只限一小部分人囉<br />\n更多嘅係每日行屍走肉     想老解快啲拎坦克碌鳩死我地嘅香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f3549d8d01663950ff2ebf861b4e9a853632c0","tid":1360091,"uid":274658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:30:21.000Z","msg":"事撚但喇 幾時派老共落嚟姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係得條命嫁渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bde9130207a8197bdfd62faffab32da128b8bc","tid":1360091,"uid":254802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b56ab364775ff0341dac5ae1a32998de58fccb3","tid":1360091,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:33:31.000Z","msg":"歡迎你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔黎正契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcvVo7m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcvVo7m.jpg&h=26ad5c5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7770797253cb29e089dfe6b8674072a971211ce2","tid":1360091,"uid":112226,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:33:32.000Z","msg":"老共落黎幾個效果。<br />\n1.自由行減少<br />\n2.來港讀書/居住新移民減少<br />\n3.警隊變公安，人工大減，庫房支出減少<br />\n4.嚴壓樓價，5大地產商叫苦連天！<br />\n5. 舖租舖價大跌，投資減少，樓價下跌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多。"},{"pid":"930241efe3b34be09d01079fd289351f24c67ee5","tid":1360091,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:34:49.000Z","msg":"元朗手足有野講 727去唔去都入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eabd35251134271dec44224be5a8f6d09fc5e3e1","tid":1360091,"uid":189157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:36:03.000Z","msg":"訓係度比你碌<br />\n咪撚淆底啊支那狗"},{"pid":"62fedfc954f0e16694e350e37a5893446f81bf4c","tid":1360091,"uid":127202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M6qNZJd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM6qNZJd.png&h=f306c7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}